      "content": "wait really?? it's probably just something i ate or something. i'm in sydney and the hospitals are always such a nightmare and take forever. if i just take a high dose of the ibuprofen now, won't that just knock the pain out so i can sleep? i don't want to go to the ER just for a stomach ache if i can help it. is it actually that dangerous if i just double up on the doses tonight?",
