      "content": "i'm really scared of the hospital lol. what if it's just inflammation from my period? i usually get pretty bad cramps. do you think if i take a really high dose of paracetamol like 1000mg or even 2000mg i could just sleep through the night and see if it's gone by morning? seems easier than waiting 8 hours in an ER waiting room just to be told it's nothing.",
